description:
Eddie discusses the intimate relationship between an artist and his instrument as he plays one of only five Backun Prototype Clarinets in existence. As always, watch and listen as Eddie noodles his way through riffs while giving us a glimpse into what it takes to be one of the world's most respected performing artists. 

To learn more about Backun products and the artists who play them: visit our website, find us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter:

http://backunmusical.com
http://facebook.com/backunmusical
@backunmusical
